  "missionVision": {
    "title": "Mission & Vision",
    "content": "Our mission is to provide a safe, inclusive, and resource-rich living environment that supports academic excellence and personal development. We focus on maintaining quality infrastructure, encouraging cultural and sporting activities, and fostering unity among residents. Hall XII strives to ensure every student feels valued, supported, and inspired to achieve their best.",
    "vision": "We envision Hall XII as a hostel that seamlessly blends tradition with modern living, becoming a symbol of unity, innovation, and pride on campus. Our goal is to create a vibrant community that excels in competitions, contributes to campus life, and preserves its unique heritage. Every resident should leave with skills, memories, and friendships that last a lifetime."
